      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "MOONLIGHT NELLIE (1) scored her maiden success two back then hit the frame last time when third and beaten 7 lengths at this track over 400m (23.64). Returns to the scene of her maiden win. In form and looks a top chance again. NATURALLY GIRL (6) missed the frame last time, finishing 4th (23.73) last time in a TG1-4W at this track. Form here at this distance is strong including three wins. Has good early speed and can overcome the tricky draw. Has ability and a bold showing is expected. CADILLAC MAGIC (2) comes off an average run last start when sixth at this track over 305m behind Lust To Burn (18.22) in a Other. Placed at her previous run. Should be in this for a long way. OLLIE LIMES (4) is in the mix despite finishing out of the placings here last start.",
